resources.string: According to the Chinese Provisions on the Scope of Necessary Personal Information for Common Types of Mobile Internet Applications, GetApps is defined as an app market, with basic features including <font color=#333e64>browsing, searching, downloading, updating, and installing apps</font>. Additional features include the use of Xiaomi Account, favorites, sharing, reporting content, pre-orders, and unlimited data features offered to Mi Mobile users. By tapping \"Agree\" below, you agree to our collection and processing of your necessary personal information, including clipboard content, in order to provide our basic services to you. We will request your consent with a pop-up dialog individually when collecting your personal information for the use of the aforementioned additional features.
